.DT
move_with_look
$MUDNAME$ creator help
move_with_look

Name
.SI 5
move_with_look - Moves a npc or player from one location to another.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
thing->move_with_look( destination, messin, messout );
.EI 5

Description
.SP 5 5
This function is the general player and monster moving command.  It
handles updating of follow chains, fight control, printing of
exit and enter messages and doing a look upon entering the
new room. It is the new replacement for move_player(), and
has the same arguments as move().
.EP 5 5
See also
.SP 5 5
move, modify_exit
.EP
